'''''Mon Valle''''' was a [[Bulk cruiser/Legends|bulk cruiser]] of the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]] during the early [[Standard year/Legends|years]] of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]].

Modified for assault, ''Mon Valle'' participated in the [[First Battle of Borleias]], acting as a platform of [[Defender Wing]]. ''Mon Valle'' was lost in the attack.

